    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve hand-crafted puzzles across multiple mechanics: from single-solution challenges and word-based doors, to strategy levels with companion robots, diamond-collecting mazes, and cryptic clue-based conundrums.<br> <br>Features: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Creative, rewarding word-based puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >'Challenging words' hidden among levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optional, progressive clue system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Built-in dictionary</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Includes Level editor</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relaxing original guitar soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Re-bindable keys</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full or windowed (fully resizable) play</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level progress and undo history persist per level</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Difficulty:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recommended English level: fluent, or alternatively intermediate, in which case the built-in dictionary and clue system will help you progress and improve your vocabulary as you play. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While the main challenge is word-based, there’s a moderately increasing Sokoban (block-pushing) element as the game progresses.</p>",
